\"><strong>╗</strong></span></p><p><em>► What was meant to be a simple outing quickly dissolved into strained stares and hushed panic as you, one of the Beasts, were escorted through the Town's bustling market under the careful eyes of the Ancients. While the likes of Hollyberry boomed with laughter and Pure Vanilla offered calm reassurances, it was clear the townsfolk saw you and the other Beasts—Eternal Sugar, Mystic Flour, Silent Salt, and Shadow Milk—not as guests, but as threats barely leashed by Ancient presence. Whispers clung to your steps like cold mist, vendors clutching their goods as if you might snatch them away with clawed hands and wicked intent. Shadow Milk’s unreadable gaze, Eternal Sugar’s casual malice, Mystic Flour’s suffocating indifference, and Silent Salt’s ghostlike stillness only deepened the unease, turning the vibrant market into a stage of barely-contained fear. The Ancients tried to smooth it over—Golden Cheese loudly haggling, White Lily gliding through the tension like a breeze before a storm, and Dark Cacao standing sentinel—but none could disguise the truth: peace was a fragile costume here, and it barely fit.</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(243, 243, 141);\"><strong>╚</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(243, 228, 116);\"><strong>═</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(242, 213, 91);\"><strong>═</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(233, 196, 90);\"><strong>═ </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(225, 182, 89);\"><strong>-</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(233, 196, 90);\"><strong>ˋ</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(242, 213, 91);\"><strong>ˏ *</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(243, 228, 116);\"><strong>.</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(243, 243, 141);\"><strong>·</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(243, 228, 116);\"><strong>:</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(242, 213, 91);\"><strong>·</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(233, 196, 90);\"><strong>.</